{
  "texts": [
    "In sign language recognition, the hand signals of the users are in the target object position.",
    "The confidence score indicates how accurately hand signals are perceived in the bounding box.",
    "In the realtime Turkish sign language detection system, the successful detection of the hand signal is determined by a value of IoU.",
    "The value of the IoU function is taken a threshold Fig. 9 Labeling data in LabelImg value determined by looking at the overlap between the predicted and the base true bounding box.",
    "For this study, the IoU threshold is set to 0.5."
  ]
}